data.description: SELLER WILL CONSIDER RATE BUY DOWN! Luxurious Home in a Beautiful Community! Relax and breathe deeply as you you take in the long lake views, with golf course beyond.  Newly painted inside and out, with granite/stainless and 42in espresso cabinetry, new fridge and microwave, there is plenty of beautiful space for entertaining. Kitchen and great room look out at the oversized lanai and solar heated pool. Spacious bedrooms and carefully appointed bathrooms will make living here a joy for you, your family, and your guests. Pool has brand new pump and filter, and can be converted to salt. It's surrounded by a no-see-um screened cage, and the covered part of the lanai extends the length of the house (rare for the area!).  Feel secure with storm shutters and battery operated hurricane lighting throughout the home. Every detail has been well thought out and finished for you - including the designer furniture. Reverse osmosis system guarantees delicious water. Laundry conveniently off kitchen. Buyers with pets are in luck! There is plenty of yard space on this oversized lot! HOA fees are some of the lowest in the area, and the amenities are plentiful!
